      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 18:45:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着杠杆ETF损失达到40％，华尔街赌徒被粉碎了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/wall-street-gamblers-get-crushed-as-leveraged-etf-losses-hit-40</link>
      <description><![CDATA[他们在途中的愤怒：高风险，高回报交易所交易的资金，由华尔街产品经理在大选后牛市的欣喜若狂造成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/wall-street-gamblers-get-crushed-as-leveraged-etf-losses-hit-40</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 18:16:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>必和必拓将开启了108亿美元的计划，以防止智利铜下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/bhp-kicks-off-10-8-billion-plan-to-prevent-chile-copper-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团将在智利启动一项巨大的108亿美元投资计划，并大修是全球最有价值的矿业公司战斗的矿石质量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/bhp-kicks-off-10-8-billion-plan-to-prevent-chile-copper-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 18:06:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>彭博公开兴趣02/25/2025</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-25/bloomberg-open-interest-02-25-2025-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以“彭博公开兴趣”的速度开始在美国交易日开始。马特·米勒（Matt Miller），凯蒂·格里菲尔德（Katie Greifeld）和索纳利·巴萨克（Sonali Basak）将您带到华尔街前往大街，前往C-Suite及其他地区。 “彭博社开放兴趣”将为您带来塑造当天叙事的领导者的市场嗡嗡声。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-25/bloomberg-open-interest-02-25-2025-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 18:02:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财务监管机构专注于影子银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-25/financial-watchdog-focuses-on-shadow-banks-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金融稳定委员会正在仔细研究影子银行，以确保它们不会引发更广泛的危机。一个新的工作组将集中在高风险领域，包括携带贸易和基础贸易。彭博社的尼尔·卡拉南（Neil Callanan）报道了“彭博社开放兴趣”。 （纠正记者的名字）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-25/financial-watchdog-focuses-on-shadow-banks-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 16:42:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Altice France，债权人附近的债权人来重组债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/altice-france-creditors-are-near-a-deal-to-restructure-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁帕特里克·德拉希（Patrick Drahi）的电信提供商Altice France接近与债权人达成协议，以将公司的债务堆积86亿欧元（90亿美元）削减，以换取非控制权股权和治理股权和治理变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/altice-france-creditors-are-near-a-deal-to-restructure-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 14:09:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Innergex从魁北克退休金收购70亿美元后飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/cdpq-agrees-to-buy-innergex-renewable-energy-for-7-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Innergex Renewable Energy Inc.在养老金经理Caisse De De De De De De De De De De De Placement Du Quebec同意以全现金交易中的价格购买加拿大的电力公司，该公司将其重视约为100亿加元（70亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/cdpq-agrees-to-buy-innergex-renewable-energy-for-7-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 13:13:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财政部产生幻灯片，因为信心量规stokes经济恐惧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/treasuries-rally-as-traders-boost-bets-on-fed-interest-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者信心的规程加入了大量证据表明，美国经济将需要今年的美联储利率削减速度，因此财政部的收益下降至周二的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-25/treasuries-rally-as-traders-boost-bets-on-fed-interest-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 09:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着经济烦恼的刺激债券集会：市场包裹，股票受到打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票受到打击，债券被激动，因为对美国消费者的又一次令人失望的阅读引起了人们对世界上最大经济体的健康的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 22:35:00 GMT</pubDate>
